Chat is very protective of the ones he loves and cares for, although there are few of these people. To most people, he appears cocky and arrogant. While this is true, he mostly uses it as a bravado against people. He is very self-assured and confident in his abilities. He doesn’t is skeptical about most things, and only believes what he can see for himself. He taught himself everything he knows, including how to make a living for himself without anyone else.

