Chat grew up on his own. He’s fairly certain he once had a family, but can’t remember who they are. He was taken into an orphanage, but soon escaped. Ever since then, he has taught himself how to burglarize people in order to make enough money for himself. One day, he was trying to sneak into a house when he was nearly caught by a girl. This girl was Marinette, and he soon developed a crush on her. Thankfully, she didn’t rat him out to her parents when he broke into her house, but rather let him off with a warning if he tried anything again. Ever since then, he has wanted to see her and meet her again.
